This paper discusses the management and optimization of wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of competition among service providers, which is related to game theory (cs.GT). The paper also discusses pricing and resource allocation, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions small-cell deployments, which are related to multimedia systems (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the impact on social welfare, which is related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
